                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-1434" type="given" value="MARK"></interp>MARK WELLS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a bombardier in the Royal Artillery at Woolwich—the prisoner was a private. About four o'clock, on 25th July, I missed these boots—I saw them safe at eight that moruing.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18480821-name-1435" type="witnessName">
