                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-1435" type="given" value="GEORGE WILLIAM"></interp>GEORGE WILLIAM WATERS</persName>
                  </hi>. These boots were pawned with me by Mrs. Smith—I gave this duplicate for them—she said they were her husband's,</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184808210205"></xptr>
               <p>but he was dead, and directly afterwards she said they were her husband's boots that was to be.</p>
