                  </hi>. I received this ticket, took it to the pawnbroker, and he stopped it—Smith followed me in, and said they were her boots, and then the prisoner ran in and said, "You are detaining my boots, are you? I will go and fetch the sergeant," and ran out.</p>
               <p>
